item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Mix with the masters - Lana Del Rey - Jack Antonoff - A&W
item.description: I’ve searched high and low for the video of mix with the masters and it’s for the song A&W by Lana Del Rey. Does anyone have it? This shit is paywalled behind like $300 it’s insane. For someone who wants to break the norms of the music industry he sure is making sure only the well off can afford to learn. I don’t have $300 to blow for a video where I might learn a thing or two.
